Description: Hange discovers that Krista is the true heir to the throne, but before she can be installed as queen, she is kidnapped.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 15
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: As this series barrels toward its conclusion, Naruto and Sasuke must work together to defeat Madara.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 69
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 6
Author: Okayado

Description: A new Turbo Duel hero named Yusei Fudo emerges from the outskirts of New Domino City and he will defeat any challenger thanks to his custom–built Duel Runner.
Title: YU-GI-OH! 5D'S, VOL. 7
Author: Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato
Contributor: by Masahiro Hikokubo and Masashi Sato

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father’s rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 8
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: Yuichiro is on a mission to kill every vampire in existence but in order to accomplish his goal, he must become a master of demon–possessed weaponry.
Title: SERAPH OF THE END, VOL. 4
Author: Takaya Kagami and Yamato Yamamoto
Contributor: by Takaya Kagami and Yamato Yamamoto

Description: A pair of Internet-savvy siblings are transported into a fantasy video game. Can they become the saviors of humanity in this new world?
Title: NO GAME, NO LIFE, VOL. 1
Author: Yuu Kamiya and Mashiro Hiiragi
Contributor: by Yuu Kamiya and Mashiro Hiiragi

Description: Nanami’s journey through time concludes, but will her newfound knowledge of the past jeopardize her relationship with Tomoe?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 17
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Tatsumi hopes to earn money for his village by working in the Capital, but that won’t be easy in a place where corruption is rampant and a league of assassins are the only good guys.
Title: AKAME GA KILL!, VOL. 1
Author: Takahiro and Tetsuya Tashiro
